comments.body:
I think this is the only case where you don't know `empty` at compile time; could rewrite it as:

```c++
void MakeKeyData() { if (!keydata) keydata = make_secure_unique<KeyType>(); }
void ClearKeyData() { keydata.reset(); }
...
if (other.keydata) {
    MakeKeyData();
    *keydata = *other.keydata;
} else {
    ClearKeyData();
}
```

